      <title>香港上市的中国股票准备应对特朗普关税的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/hong-kong-listed-chinese-stocks-brace-for-trump-tariffs-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普打响关税战的第一枪后，在香港上市的中国股票在休市三个交易日后于周一恢复交易时将面临新的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/hong-kong-listed-chinese-stocks-brace-for-trump-tariffs-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 07:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非能源储备恢复 暂停停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/south-africa-suspends-power-cuts-as-energy-reserves-recover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家电力公司 Eskom 已暂停从周五开始的轮流停电，理由是紧急储备已恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/south-africa-suspends-power-cuts-as-energy-reserves-recover</guid>
